    `iban` STRING COMMENT 'The International Bank Account Number for the counterparty, used for international wire transfers.',
    `incorporation_country_code` STRING COMMENT 'The three-letter ISO country code where the counterparty entity is legally incorporated or registered.',
    `incorporation_date` DATE COMMENT 'The date on which the counterparty entity was legally incorporated or registered.',
    `industry_code` STRING COMMENT 'The standard industry classification code (NAICS or SIC) representing the counterpartys primary business activity.',
    `is_related_party` BOOLEAN COMMENT 'Boolean flag indicating whether this counterparty is a related party under accounting standards (e.g., subsidiary, affiliate, key management personnel).',
